<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Profile Card</title>
    
    <style>
        /* Universal Reset: Poori window ki default margin/padding hatane ke liye */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Body Styling: Card ko screen ke bilkul center mein lane ke liye */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f2f5; /* Light gray background */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Profile Card Layout */
        .profile-card {
            background-color: #ffffff; /* Card ka white background */
            width: 350px;
            padding: 30px; /* Card ke andar ka space */
            margin: 20px; /* Card ke baahar ka space */
            border-radius: 16px; /* Smooth rounded corners */
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Floating look dene ke liye shadow */
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; /* Light border line */
        }

        /* Profile Image Styling */
        .profile-img {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%; /* Image ko perfectly round/circular banane ke liye */
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 4px solid #4f46e5; /* Image ke baahar attractive purple border */
        }

        /* Text and Typography Styling */
        .profile-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .profile-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4f46e5; /* Accent color matching the border */
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .profile-bio {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        /* Button Link Styling */
        .profile-btn {
            display: inline-block; /* Link ko button jaisa block banane ke liye */
            text-decoration: none; /* Link ke neeche ki underline hatane ke liye */
            background-color: #4f46e5;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-radius: 25px; /* Pill-shaped button */
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease; /* Hover smooth karne ke liye */
        }

        /* Button Hover Effect */
        .profile-btn:hover {
            background-color: #3730a3; /* Hover karne par dark color */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="profile-card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Profile Picture" class="profile-img">
        
        <h2 class="profile-name">GOURAV</h2>
        <p class="profile-title">SOFTWARE DEVELOPER</p>
        <p class="profile-bio">Software is a set of digital instructions that tells computer hardware exactly what to do. Without it, a device is useless. You can easily divide all software into two main types: System Software and Application Software</p>
        
        <a href="https://students.optimizelabs.io/register" target="_blank" class="profile-btn">Connect</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
